{"id": "art-1534", "label": "Art. 1534", "title": "Art. 1534", "slug": "art-1534", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_409904535\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2125\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_409904535\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 153<sup>4</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_372890908\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2124\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_372890908\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Cel <span class=SpellE>pu&#355;in</span> o dat&#259; la\n3 luni, directoratul prezint&#259; un raport scris consiliului de supraveghere\ncu privire la conducerea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, cu\nprivire la activitatea acesteia <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> la posibila\nsa <span class=SpellE>evolu&#355;ie</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1674172475\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2123\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1674172475\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Pe lâng&#259; informarea periodic&#259;\nprev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (1), directoratul comunic&#259; în timp util\nconsiliului de supraveghere orice <span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ie</span> cu\nprivire la evenimentele ce ar putea avea o <span class=SpellE>influen&#355;&#259;</span>\nsemnificativ&#259; asupra <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;iei</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_157127798\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2122\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_157127798\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Consiliul de supraveghere poate solicita directoratului\norice <span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> pe care le consider&#259;\nnecesare pentru exercitarea <span class=SpellE>atribu&#355;iilor</span> sale de\ncontrol <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> poate efectua verific&#259;ri <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>investiga&#355;ii</span>\ncorespunz&#259;toare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1877818674\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2121\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1877818674\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Fiecare membru al consiliului de supraveghere are acces\nla <span class=SpellE>informa&#355;iile</span> transmise consiliului.</span></p>"}